  "text": "Unlike RADX depletion, FBH1 depletion in BRCA2-deficient cells does not rescue replication fork protection due to HU treatment [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . However, FBH1 depletion in cells deficient for the fork protection factors BOD1L or WRN IP1 does rescue nascent strand degradation of stalled replication forks [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
